import {
  Container,
  Row,
  Col,
  Form,
  Button,
  Card,
  InputGroup,
  DropdownButton,
  Dropdown,
} from "react-bootstrap";

import React from "react";

export default function StoreCard({ store }) {
  return (
    <Card className="h-60">
      <Row>
        <Col xs={5}>
          <Card.Img variant="top" src={store.image} style={{ width: "100%" }} />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={7}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>{store.name}</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{store.description}</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{store.rating} stars</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{store.store}</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{store.distance} miles from your location</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>{store.location}</Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>${store.price}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Card>
  );
}
